Action items
Example Copilot Prompts for Word
1. Create Executive Summary
Create an executive summary for leadership highlighting workflow inefficiencies, compliance risks, KPI trends, and operational improvement opportunities.
2. Generate Full Operational Report
Create a professional operational assessment report using the provided workflow analysis, compliance findings, KPI trends, and meeting summaries. Include recommendations and next steps.
3. Create Risk Assessment Section
Generate a risk assessment section summarizing high-risk operational areas, overdue compliance items, and workflow bottlenecks.
4. Create Recommendations Section
Create actionable recommendations to improve workflow efficiency, compliance tracking, reporting automation, and cross-team collaboration.
5. Create Action Plan Table
Generate an action plan table including issue, recommendation, owner, priority, and target completion date.
